options.text: Can you teach me the basics of cooking please?
Tell me about different food I can make.

c3783297-9474-40ba-a0c4-9220e52fa288.title: <player>
c3783297-9474-40ba-a0c4-9220e52fa288.text: Can you teach me the basics of cooking please?

fe3b62af-7c35-4913-8091-c6eeffad95e0.title: Cooking tutor
fe3b62af-7c35-4913-8091-c6eeffad95e0.text: The simplest thing to cook is raw meat or fish.

f636d95d-c7e4-4819-a363-72c9f81cdc20.title: Cooking tutor
f636d95d-c7e4-4819-a363-72c9f81cdc20.text:
Fish can be caught, speak to the fishing tutor south of
here in the swamp. Killing cows or chickens will yield
raw meat to cook too.

068f7799-ee05-4ed8-94b6-cbac81867072.title: Cooking tutor
068f7799-ee05-4ed8-94b6-cbac81867072.text:
When you have a full inventory of meat or fish, find a
range. Look for this icon on your minimap.

ab6676aa-1405-40b2-8646-56697a6ee1b6.title: Cooking tutor
ab6676aa-1405-40b2-8646-56697a6ee1b6.text:
You can use your own fire... but it's not as effective
and you'll burn more. To build a fire use a tinderbox
on logs.

043700a6-27e7-43d0-843a-2c136a2ef868.title: Cooking tutor
043700a6-27e7-43d0-843a-2c136a2ef868.text:
Once you've found your range, click on it. This will
bring up a menu of the food you can cook.

2787359f-c5e9-4355-879c-ee48619f2c87.title: Cooking tutor
2787359f-c5e9-4355-879c-ee48619f2c87.text:
When you have a full inventory of cooked food, drop
the useless burnt food and find a bank. Look for this
symbol on your minimap after climbing the stairs of the
Lumbridge Castle to the top. There are numerous

00aaab6c-b9f1-4b5f-a360-1f31ae75d5b7.title: Cooking tutor
00aaab6c-b9f1-4b5f-a360-1f31ae75d5b7.text: banks around the world, all marked with that symbol.

383b0aed-5a29-4136-b07f-7f644e96a5e9.title: Cooking tutor
383b0aed-5a29-4136-b07f-7f644e96a5e9.text:
If you're interested in quests, I heard my friend the
cook in Lumbridge Castle is in need of a hand. Just
talk to him and he'll set you off.

3295d935-5e97-4e3c-bc21-661e341a0f5e.title: Cooking tutor
3295d935-5e97-4e3c-bc21-661e341a0f5e.text:
Fish and meat of most varieties can be cooked very
simply on either a fire or range, experiment which one
works for you.

73510888-4e76-452c-8340-ce1ed8bec881.title: Cooking tutor
73510888-4e76-452c-8340-ce1ed8bec881.text:
Use a pot of flour with a bucket of water. You will then
get an option to make bread dough, pitta bread dough,
pastry dough, or pizza dough. Select pizza or pastry
dough.

d575b51c-8073-4b65-a70c-bc4f6003feeb.title: Cooking tutor
d575b51c-8073-4b65-a70c-bc4f6003feeb.text:
Use the pastry dough with a pie dish then add your
filling such as apple or red berries.

d86579a2-ce8e-4200-a80b-e908f3f1e16e.title: Cooking tutor
d86579a2-ce8e-4200-a80b-e908f3f1e16e.text:
Finally cook your pie by using the unbaked pie on a
cooking range. Mmmm...pie.

041b147e-d61b-40fb-99ec-3135f6c0720a.title: Cooking tutor
041b147e-d61b-40fb-99ec-3135f6c0720a.text:
There's pizza too! Find yourself some tomato and
cheese, use on the Pizza dough. Cook the pizza on a
range then add any other toppings you want, such as
anchovies.
